{"tid":582753,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"連登評選最正常女youtuber catgirl唔好嬲豬啦😢","createTime":"2018-03-06T12:26:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T12:36:07.000Z","uid":24050,"like":58,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"1be7d29a2a1f16a4f7f7ee6cc384de5c20ebb484","tid":582753,"uid":24050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:26:40.000Z","msg":"阿ken買左啲攝影器材 成段開箱片自high<br />\n激到catgirl西囇面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/194832_90537db163a0d2a6015d50ed267454e9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F194832_90537db163a0d2a6015d50ed267454e9.png&h=ec7f19b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲人喺片下面留comment攻擊catgirl bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/195313_afaf9bb49be103d5451801d78ad2830e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F195313_afaf9bb49be103d5451801d78ad2830e.png&h=94bf516f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你班香港人無啲幽默感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/195411_dd3d159b3113e38875c321b20dd55aab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F195411_dd3d159b3113e38875c321b20dd55aab.png&h=f3d6461f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔鐘意就唔好睇！<br />\n唔准攻擊youtube界唯一清泉catgirl bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">其實我真係段段片都睇<br />\n以為佢真係對人啲comment睇得好開<br />\n點知今次段片就露真身<br />\n淨係like讚佢嗰啲comment<br />\n負面嘅就串柒柒咁回應<br />\n段片入面同啲comment都show到佢擺明堅嬲<br />\n人地善意意見叫佢唔好嬲攝影師<br />\n佢就起曬gong話人地睇佢啲片太認真無幽默感<br />\n真心失望 如果咁介意人地講咩就唔好扮豁達啦<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"746c5cb97c845d3020866a1c0b42a5540399c493","tid":582753,"uid":163911,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:28:08.000Z","msg":"佢真係好樣衰"},{"pid":"0d39547151b94561a918ccf63c1687a4668ee347","tid":582753,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:30:25.000Z","msg":"唔鐘意咪唔好 __ 囉"},{"pid":"5306846b1439a7ac7bb8fc3a37890b6ccc76a30f","tid":582753,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:31:11.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 屁屁洗腦超人⛷"},{"pid":"a026b416cca22eb1e17aace6bd9e76fc0e9f4a7e","tid":582753,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5306846b1439a7ac7bb8fc3a37890b6ccc76a30f","tid":582753,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:31:11.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 屁屁洗腦超人⛷"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:33:53.000Z","msg":"Cat girl 都攞上來講，唔block 等幾時！"},{"pid":"7b3d353a6560981250b4e5fe446a3b8cad56866e","tid":582753,"uid":162043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a026b416cca22eb1e17aace6bd9e76fc0e9f4a7e","tid":582753,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5306846b1439a7ac7bb8fc3a37890b6ccc76a30f","tid":582753,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:31:11.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 屁屁洗腦超人⛷"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:33:53.000Z","msg":"Cat girl 都攞上來講，唔block 等幾時！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:37:47.000Z","msg":"幫條垃圾豬閪做宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9e652d10d6a2a040dc87af3b23c9ca344518697","tid":582753,"uid":171594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:42:51.000Z","msg":"咁撚肥<br />\n老d就知死"},{"pid":"c4b601b65b14bf01f2b1565dc31d979eab9c00de","tid":582753,"uid":132587,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:59:06.000Z","m